                </h2>
                <p>
                    While every organization is unique, we’ve compiled some common patterns of business behavior relative to each stage of the decision automation journey. In this report, risks and returns are presented with each stage, providing insight into the potential ROI impact from moving to the next step in your journey.
                </p>
