                        <b>Potential return from moving to the next stage:</b> Reduced operational risk for the business due to employee turnover. No more privatizing knowledge.
                    </p>
                    <p>Do you want to learn more about taking the next step after Stage 0? Then check out our post on <a href="https://inrule.com/business-rules-engine/" onclick="window.open(this.href,_blank); return false;" onkeypress="window.open(this.href); return false;">What is the InRule Business Rules Engine?</a></p>
